    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TropTopia is a 2D single-player and local co-op game where you make your way through levels filled with obstacles and enemies trying to stop you from collecting all the fruits. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game features awesome mechanics such as wall jump, wall slide, double jump and coyote jump! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285240/extras/c5afd25ed44f50f3ec1b12d12f7fdc62.poster.avif?t=1738081668\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285240/extras/c5afd25ed44f50f3ec1b12d12f7fdc62.webm?t=1738081668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285240/extras/c5afd25ed44f50f3ec1b12d12f7fdc62.mp4?t=1738081668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TropTopia even has a skin selection menu where you buy skins with the fruits you have collected!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285240/extras/974e8bb0a1c100f05192c2b77a131e70.poster.avif?t=1738081668\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285240/extras/974e8bb0a1c100f05192c2b77a131e70.webm?t=1738081668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285240/extras/974e8bb0a1c100f05192c2b77a131e70.mp4?t=1738081668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TropTopia also offers 3 difficultys for those who want a challange!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285240/extras/b37b2a124905431a3bda7f6b4b5c7cef.poster.avif?t=1738081668\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285240/extras/b37b2a124905431a3bda7f6b4b5c7cef.webm?t=1738081668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285240/extras/b37b2a124905431a3bda7f6b4b5c7cef.mp4?t=1738081668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
